&lt;div class=&quot;styles--2BkR3&quot; data-ui=&quot;job-description&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a strategic thinker who loves unlocking growth through data-driven performance marketing? Do you get excited about optimizing campaigns, relentlessly testing new strategies, and uncovering insights that drive massive results? Does scaling acquisition efficiently and automating for impact sound like your ideal challenge? If so, we want to talk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TurboTenant is looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Paid Search Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to be a driving force behind our growth engine. You’ll play a key role in building the nation’s best community of landlords by driving high-quality growth through strategic, highly analytical, and creative paid search campaigns.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t just about managing budgets; it’s about breaking down walls, transforming complex data into a true competitive advantage, and fostering a high-velocity culture of operational excellence across our Performance Marketing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid Search Strategy &amp;amp; Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Fully own, administer, and manage TurboTenant’s entire Google and Bing Ad ecosystem across multiple brands, focusing relentlessly on driving profitable new user signups and customer acquisition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign Expansion &amp;amp; Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead in-depth campaign expansion and testing. Optimize bidding algorithms, ad copy, and quality scores, while expanding keywords to efficiently scale budgets and hit company-wide growth goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Funnel Mastery &amp;amp; Analytics:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with marketing and product teams to identify new opportunities, refine lead loops, and better understand the needs of landlords and tenants to optimize every conversion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner directly with Google and Bing representatives to secure custom reporting and gain access to exclusive beta programs. Translate complex channel data into clear insights that explain how paid search impacts the broader business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience to Dominate:&lt;/strong&gt; 4+ years of experience owning Paid Search specifically for B2C companies, with a proven track record of driving profitable revenue and user acquisition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Budget Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Demonstrated experience scaling and managing monthly budgets in excess of $300k.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytical &amp;amp; Data Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; A passion for clear, concise communication that is consistently backed by data. You can own the accuracy of channel data and build complex analyses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agile &amp;amp; Collaborative Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; A collaborative spirit and a willingness to test new ideas, learn from results, and proactively work cross-functionally to drive feature adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Savvy:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong foundational knowledge of Google Ads conversion tracking and offline conversion imports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Bonus Superpowers:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone with a modern, tech-forward approach:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Native Workflow:&lt;/strong&gt; You’re ahead of the curve, utilizing AI tools (like Cursor, Claude, or ChatGPT) to accelerate your productivity, campaign execution, and data analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GTM &amp;amp; Tracking Depth:&lt;/strong&gt; Advanced experience with Google Tag Manager (GTM) for custom event tracking and conversion setup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real Estate Experienc
